[B]TV Shows are based on the media found in Kodi's Library[/B]

[COLOR=blue][B]TV Show:[/B][/COLOR] - Select preferred TV Show.

[COLOR=blue][B]Show in Order:[/B][/COLOR] - Places shows in order by episode. If you want Shows to play in sequential order without skipping episodes select "Unlimited" media limit.

TV Show information is provided by Kodi, if you have issues with the data provided use PseudoTV Live's Window Channel manager or a Kodi web interface such as "WiMM" to amend the metadata.